              "prompt": "Explore the codebase at D:\\github\\绌洪棿鏁版嵁妫€鏌ユ闈㈢増-涓婚-design thoroughly. I need to understand:\n\n1. The overall project structure - what framework is used, key directories\n2. The current theme system - how themes are defined, switched, and applied\n3. The color schemes for each theme (sunrise, gradient, glass, forest, aurora, dark)\n4. How the settings page currently presents theme options\n5. Any CSS variables, theme configuration files\n\nPlease provide:\n- Directory structure (top 3 levels)\n- The full content of theme-related files\n- The settings page code\n- Any theme configuration or constants files\n- How CSS variables are currently used for theming\n\nBe very thorough - read all relevant files completely.",
